   <abstract>Reporter Leslie Ackerson saw people packing up to leave. They were packing photo albums, paintings, and other precious things. One woman spoke to Leslie about having to leave her piano behind. Evacuating for an imminent fire causes you to think about what has true meaning in your life. What you will bring and things you must leave behind. Sometimes the things that you leave are just as meaningful, but too large to bring with you. 
</abstract>
